function App() {
  const [sortConfig, setSortConfig] = useState({ key: 'Niveau', direction: 'asc' });
  const [searchTerm, setSearchTerm] = useState('');

  const handleSort = (key) => {
    setSortConfig(prev => ({
      key,
      direction: prev.key === key && prev.direction === 'asc' ? 'desc' : 'asc'
    }));
  };

  const filteredAndSortedData = React.useMemo(() => {
    let result = [...monstersData];

    // Filtrage
    if (searchTerm) {
      result = result.filter(item =>
        Object.values(item).some(value =>
          value.toString().toLowerCase().includes(searchTerm.toLowerCase())
        )
      );
    }

    // Tri
    if (sortConfig.key) {
      result.sort((a, b) => {
        const direction = sortConfig.direction === 'asc' ? 1 : -1;
        
        if (typeof a[sortConfig.key] === 'number') {
          return (a[sortConfig.key] - b[sortConfig.key]) * direction;
        }
        
        return a[sortConfig.key].localeCompare(b[sortConfig.key]) * direction;
      });
    }

    return result;
  }, [searchTerm, sortConfig]);

  const stats = React.useMemo(() => {
    const uniqueZones = new Set(filteredAndSortedData.map(item => item.Zone)).size;
    const totalMonsters = filteredAndSortedData.length;
    const averageLevel = Math.round(
      filteredAndSortedData.reduce((acc, curr) => acc + curr.Niveau, 0) / totalMonsters
    );

    return { uniqueZones, totalMonsters, averageLevel };
  }, [filteredAndSortedData]);

  return (
    <div className="min-h-screen bg-gray-50 p-4">
      <div className="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        {/* Header */}
        <div className="mb-8">
          <h1 className="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
            Guide des Monstres Dofus
          </h1>
          <p className="text-gray-600">
            Base de données complète des monstres et leurs zones
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* Stats Cards */}
        <div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-6">
          <div className="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
            <h3 className="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500">Total Monstres</h3>
            <p className="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-600">{stats.totalMonsters}</p>
          </div>
          <div className="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
            <h3 className="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500">Zones Uniques</h3>
            <p className="text-2xl font-semibold text-green-600">{stats.uniqueZones}</p>
          </div>
          <div className="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
            <h3 className="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500">Niveau Moyen</h3>
            <p className="text-2xl font-semibold text-purple-600">{stats.averageLevel}</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Search Bar */}
        <div className="mb-6">
          <input
            type="text"
            placeholder="Rechercher un monstre ou une zone..."
            className="w-full p-3 border rounded-lg shadow-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500"
            value={searchTerm}
            onChange={(e) => setSearchTerm(e.target.value)}
          />
        </div>

        {/* Table */}
        <div className="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
          <div className="overflow-x-auto">
            <table className="min-w-full divide-y divide-gray-200">
              <thead className="bg-gray-50">
                <tr>
                  {['Zone', 'Monstre', 'Niveau'].map((key) => (
                    <th
                      key={key}
                      onClick={() => handleSort(key)}
                      className="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-100"
                    >
                      <div className="flex items-center">
                        {key}
                        {sortConfig.key === key && (
                          <span className="ml-2">
                            {sortConfig.direction === 'asc' ? '↑' : '↓'}
                          </span>
                        )}
                      </div>
                    </th>
                  ))}
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody className="bg-white divide-y divide-gray-200">
                {filteredAndSortedData.map((item, index) => (
                  <tr 
                    key={index}
                    className="hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors"
                  >
                    <td className="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm text-gray-900">
                      {item.Zone}
                    </td>
                    <td className="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm text-gray-900">
                      {item.Monstre}
                    </td>
                    <td className="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm text-gray-900">
                      {item.Niveau}
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                ))}
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Footer */}
        <div className="mt-4 text-center text-sm text-gray-500">
          Total affiché : {filteredAndSortedData.length} monstre(s)
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  );
}

export default App;
